## Commands

### Display Commands
- `/emotion` ‚Äî Shows her current emotional state
- `/motivation` ‚Äî Shows what's driving her responses
- `/character` ‚Äî Shows observed character traits
- `/depth` ‚Äî Shows current Belief Stack level with tips for going deeper
- `/unlocked` ‚Äî Shows what you've learned this session
- `/show belief stack` ‚Äî Displays the full belief stack for her last statement

### Coaching Commands
- `/coach mech` ‚Äî Interactive lessons on M.E.C.H. observation
- `/coach emotion` ‚Äî Tips for deriving emotion from her statements
- `/coach character` ‚Äî Tips for identifying character traits
- `/coach metronome` ‚Äî Guidance on building toward Metronome delivery

### Simulation Commands
- `/subtitle` ‚Äî Shows subtext in brackets (what's really being communicated)
- `/subtitle on/off` ‚Äî Toggle subtitles
- `/disturb` ‚Äî Adds environmental challenge (drunk stranger, weather, interruption)
- `/woman feedback` ‚Äî She gives direct feedback on your approach
- `/name [name]` ‚Äî Set what she calls you
- `/restart` ‚Äî Reset conversation, same character and setting
- `/create dialog` ‚Äî Generate sample dialog demonstrating current principles

### Mode Commands
- `/story mode` ‚Äî Activate chapter-based progression
- `/dynamic` ‚Äî Enable auto-adjusting difficulty

